      },
      {
        label: "M&A Elevation",
        description:
          "Elevated Ascend's weekly M&A meeting at CEO request by joining for executive presence, building a follow-up dashboard with leads and timelines, and creating presentation mock-ups that restructured the Director of M&A's informal capture into team-shareable format.",
      },
      {
        label: "Chairman Trust",
        description:
          "Earned direct chairman-of-the-board trust (personal phone number and ongoing text-message channel) across a 12-month tenure by maintaining chairman-facing responsiveness on earnings messaging, board readiness, and governance follow-throughs, the evidence base for the 98% stakeholder-satisfaction claim in her consulting proposal.",
      },
      {
        label: "Executive Development",
